FIRST Jet Service in the U. S. A. . . .
4½ Hours Coast to Coast!

American JETfreight -
More Speed, More Capacity than ever before known
American's new Jet Fleet brings into being a whole new concept of transportation for goods as well as passengers.
Never before has it been possible to offer such speed and such carrying capacity to air shippers. JETfreight auto-
matically makes shipping by American an expedited service, in many cases, twice as fast.
Equally important is the carrying capacity of Jet Flagships. The 707 has tremendous Airfreight lift — the great-
est of any combination plane ever in service. Door openings are larger, to accommodate larger items. And this
cargo capacity, this speed, is available on every Jet Flagship flight.
Soon you can travel and ship on American's Jet Fleet-the latest achievement
in a long tradition of the finest in air service. Wherever you go, whatever you
ship, an American Airlines Flagship is the distinctive, dependable way..•
assuring you of the utmost in comfort, service and dependability, coupled with
unmatched frequency of convenient departure times.
AMERICAN AIRLINES
FIRST WITH JETS IN THE U.S. A.
Passengers boarding the Jet-Powered Flagship Electra
look forward to a relaxing, quiet flight — a new and wonderful Jet-Age experience.
